The paper deals with online learning and optimization in non-convex settings, which are core topics in machine learning (cs.LG) and game theory (cs.GT). The paper also mentions the use of an offline optimization oracle, which is a common technique in artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and optimization (cs.DS). Finally, the paper discusses the computation of equilibria, which is a topic in control systems (cs.SY).
